it's actually a lot like how we are now.

315
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:29,700
Yeah.

316
00:17:30,267 --> 00:17:32,067
It doesn't feel all that different.

317
00:17:32,067 --> 00:17:33,167
It doesn't feel all that different.

318
00:17:33,167 --> 00:17:35,167
Or something like that.

319
00:17:35,167 --> 00:17:37,433
That's how it is for me.

320
00:17:40,667 --> 00:17:42,567
Spending this time together has made me realize

321
00:17:42,567 --> 00:17:43,333
that actually, compared to how you were in the cabin,

322
00:17:43,333 --> 00:17:44,667
actually, compared to how you were in the cabin,

323
