467
00:24:49,167 --> 00:24:50,200
Okay, it suits you.

468
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:52,333
Not bad, right?

469
00:24:52,333 --> 00:24:53,433
Okay, this one looks good.

470
00:24:53,433 --> 00:24:54,200
Give it to me.

471
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:56,133
