476
00:25:07,167 --> 00:25:09,200
This one is really so cute.

477
00:25:11,267 --> 00:25:13,067
This God of Wealth is so cute.

478
00:25:22,367 --> 00:25:22,667
It's kind of cute.

479
00:25:22,667 --> 00:25:23,367
Tasty, right?

480
00:25:23,367 --> 00:25:24,533
It really is pretty good.

481
00:25:25,267 --> 00:25:27,000
