523
00:27:05,767 --> 00:27:06,767
You look like this one.

524
00:27:06,767 --> 00:27:07,567
Why?

525
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:11,300
Because you're really skilled.

526
00:27:13,667 --> 00:27:14,200
What?

527
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:14,733
How so?

528
00:27:14,733 --> 00:27:17,133
Alright.

529
00:27:17,133 --> 00:27:18,700
This one is perfect, I'll give you a hundred points for it.

530
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:20,433
I picked it right away.

531
00:27:20,433 --> 00:27:22,333
Fits me, since I do chores at home.

532
00:27:22,333 --> 00:27:24,100
No, that's not what I meant.

533
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,233
I meant you're awesome.

534
00:27:25,233 --> 00:27:26,100
You're really skilled.

535
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,400
You mean I'm good at chores?

536
00:27:29,733 --> 00:27:31,233
Which one looks most like you?

537
00:27:31,233 --> 00:27:32,633
The one with two brushes.

538
00:27:34,133 --> 00:27:35,733
Saying you look like a brush.

539
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,400
Now I suddenly want to sing "Wash Wash Wash."

540
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:40,700
Mermaid.

541
00:27:40,700 --> 00:27:42,100
Merman.

542
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:46,500
I'm thinking,

543
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:49,500
if you wore that tail,

544
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:53,733
