545
00:27:53,733 --> 00:27:55,300
Probably not many people.

546
00:27:56,133 --> 00:27:58,000
They all practice.

547
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,133
See the mermaids?

548
00:28:09,333 --> 00:28:10,800
They can hold their breath for so long.

549
00:28:11,733 --> 00:28:13,567
And look, she's still smiling.

550
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:24,133
I really like this song too.

551
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,067
It's when I see you.

552
00:28:26,067 --> 00:28:28,533
You don't need to say anything more.

553
00:28:38,167 --> 00:28:39,200
So tall.

554
00:28:40,033 --> 00:28:42,233
This dolphin is impressive.

555
00:28:42,233 --> 00:28:44,067
