556
00:28:44,067 --> 00:28:45,800
Who did you come with today?

557
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:47,200
With my girlfriend.

558
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:49,467
You came with your girlfriend?

559
00:28:49,467 --> 00:28:50,500
