564
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,467
I think they're really bold with their questions.

565
00:29:00,467 --> 00:29:01,600
My girlfriend's kisses are better.

566
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:03,667
Or is the dolphin's kiss better?

567
00:29:03,667 --> 00:29:05,800
If it were me, I'd say the dolphin's kiss is better.

568
00:29:07,100 --> 00:29:08,633
Yeah, because your girlfriend doesn't kiss you.

569
00:29:14,667 --> 00:29:16,067
What's with that?

570
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:20,100
It's so fierce.

